KeySequence Widget
=================

Here is a KeySequence Widget, similar to QKeySequenceEdit but slightly better

    
    
Demonstration
-------------

A simple demo of the widget is provided in ./keysequence_widget_demo


Using it in a project
---------------------

Include the keysequence_widget.pri file in the QMake project file. 
All the required files are in ./src


Installing as a Qt Designer/Creator Plugin
------------------------------------------

The sources for the designer plugin are in ./keysequence_widget_designer_plugin

Compile the library and install in
(Qt SDK)/Tools/QtCreator/bin/designer/
(Qt SDK)/(Qt Version)/(Toolchain)/plugins/designer

cd keysequence_widget_designer_plugin && qmake && make && make install

(make install may require root access)


Latest Version
--------------

The latest version of the sources can be found at the following locations
https://github.com/mbasaglia/Qt-KeySequence-Widget
git://github.com/mbasaglia/Qt-KeySequence-Widget.git


